  {"tool": "discovery", "status": "discovery", "detail": "PATTERN: cli.py:1387 validates result.get('data') against return_schema. Many tool configs incorrectly wrap content in {data: {...}, metadata: {...}} inside oneOf. The schema should describe the DATA VALUE directly, not the outer wrapper. Fix: extract oneOf[0].properties.data and use as return_schema. Affects all Ensembl tools (16+), EOL (4, fixed), FlyBase (6, fixed), FDAGSRS (3), likely many more."},
